== 獎牌榜 ==
以下獎牌榜是統計在歷屆奧運會水球比賽（1900年－2020年）獲得過獎牌的國家及地區，資料來源：<ref>{{cite web
|title=HistoFINA – Water polo medalists and statistics
|url=https://resources.fina.org/fina/document/2021/02/20/232cd7f6-8cd2-4b12-93fd-ec8f785b0726/histofina_wp_2019_final.pdf
|website=fina.org
|publisher=[[FINA|FINA]]
|date=September 2019
|format=PDF
|page=
|access-date=2021-09-05
|archive-date=2021-08-01
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801030719/https://resources.fina.org/fina/document/2021/02/20/232cd7f6-8cd2-4b12-93fd-ec8f785b0726/histofina_wp_2019_final.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>

